## Orange performance guarantee — default ON

- Include the orange banner for **both Closer and Setter** on every new invoice.  
- Markup: **`enrollment-guarantee-banner enrollment-guarantee-banner--pre-terms`**.  
- Position: directly under **Program Investment**, **above** the Terms gate.  
- Copy: duplicate from **`htsa-enrollment-zachary-taylor.html`** / **`htsa-enrollment-chad-aleo.html`** (do not freestyle legal tone).  
- **Omit only if** CJ explicitly says **“no guarantee”** or **“omit orange guarantee.”**

