## Program Investment — fixed section order

1. **Program Investment** heading  
2. **Orange performance guarantee** (unless explicitly omitted)  
3. **Terms agreement gate** (`#hts-terms-agreement-panel`): PDF → clarifications → checkbox → **Record agreement & unlock payments**  
4. **Locked** `#invest-pay-zone`: **all** Whop checkouts, payment plans, ClarityPay, Flexxbuy, **Splitit** (when on page), and optional **PayVa** only when CJ requested  

**Core rule:** No payment or financing action works until **`recordTermsAgreement`** succeeds. Locked zone uses **`invest-pay-zone`** + **`invest-pay-zone--locked`** until then; intercept **`a.invest-btn`** (including **`secondary`**). **`sessionStorage`** unlock for that tab — unique key:

```text
hts_terms_gate_<firstname>_<lastname>_v1
```

**Gated destinations (non-exhaustive):** Whop **PIF**, Whop **installment** checkouts, **ClarityPay**, **Flexxbuy**, **PayVa** (only if CJ says **PayVa**), **Splitit** (when on page — **not** on **`htsa-placement-01`**; other closer cash shells include it under PIF unless CJ says **no Splitit**), any future checkout or pre-qual link.

